sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant KServeRouter as KServe Router<br/>(Platform Ingress)
    participant HTTP as vLLM HTTP API<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant GRPC as TGIS gRPC Server<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant Engine as vLLM Inference Engine
    participant Spyre as IBM Spyre<br/>Accelerator
    participant Storage as Model Storage<br/>(S3 / PVC / HF Hub)

    Note over Engine,Storage: Flow 3: Model Loading at Startup
    Engine->>Storage: Download model weights<br/>HTTPS/443 or filesystem<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / AWS IAM
    Storage-->>Engine: Model artifacts
    Engine->>Spyre: Load model onto accelerator<br/>Hardware interface
    Spyre-->>Engine: Model ready

    Note over Client,Spyre: Flow 1: HTTP Inference Request
    Client->>KServeRouter: POST /v1/completions<br/>Auth enforced at ingress
    KServeRouter->>HTTP: Forward request<br/>8000/TCP HTTP (in-cluster)
    HTTP->>Engine: Inference request
    Engine->>Spyre: Execute inference<br/>Hardware interface
    Spyre-->>Engine: Inference result
    Engine-->>HTTP: Completion response
    HTTP-->>KServeRouter: JSON response
    KServeRouter-->>Client: Response

    Note over Client,Spyre: Flow 2: gRPC/TGIS Inference Request
    Client->>KServeRouter: gRPC GenerationService call<br/>Auth enforced at ingress
    KServeRouter->>GRPC: Forward request<br/>8033/TCP gRPC (in-cluster)
    GRPC->>Engine: Inference request
    Engine->>Spyre: Execute inference<br/>Hardware interface
    Spyre-->>Engine: Inference result
    Engine-->>GRPC: Generation response
    GRPC-->>KServeRouter: gRPC response
    KServeRouter-->>Client: Response
